<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">

<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta http-equiv="X-UA-Compatible" content="IE=edge">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>About Us | Learnen</title>
    <link href="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.3.0-alpha1/dist/css/bootstrap.min.css" rel="stylesheet"
        integrity="sha384-GLhlTQ8iRABdZLl6O3oVMWSktQOp6b7In1Zl3/Jr59b6EGGoI1aFkw7cmDA6j6gD" crossorigin="anonymous">
    <script src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.3.0-alpha1/dist/js/bootstrap.bundle.min.js"
        integrity="sha384-w76AqPfDkMBDXo30jS1Sgez6pr3x5MlQ1ZAGC+nuZB+EYdgRZgiwxhTBTkF7CXvN"
        crossorigin="anonymous"></script>
    <script src="https://kit.fontawesome.com/8182a1e71b.js" crossorigin="anonymous"></script>
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="/styles/aboutUs_styles.css">
</head>

<body>
    <div id="header">
        <%- include('navbar'); %>
    </div>

    <div class="banner">
        <div class="wrapper">
            <p class="focus-in-expand-fwd">About Us</p>
        </div>
        <div class="caption-wrapper ">
            <p class="caption typewriter" id="caption">Learnen is a place for passionate teachers and curious students
                to share knowledge!</p>
        </div>
    </div>


    <section id="about">
        <div class="about-1">
            <h1>LEARNEN</h1>
            <p>
                "Lernen" is a German verb that means "to learn" in English. It is a fundamental word in the German language and is used to describe the process of acquiring knowledge or skills through study, instruction, or experience.
            </p>
        </div>

        <div class="about-2">
            <div class="content-box-lg">
                <div class="container">
                    <div class="row">
                        <div class="col-md-4">
                            <div class="about-item text-center">
                                <i class="fa fa-book"></i>
                                <h3>MISSION</h3>
                                <hr>
                                <p>
                                    The mission of lernen is to provide individuals with access to high-quality educational content and resources that can help them acquire new skills, knowledge, and competencies. Lernen use technology to deliver learning experiences that are accessible, engaging, and flexible. Lernen can provide a range of learning opportunities, from traditional academic courses.
                                </p>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                        <div class="col-md-4">
                            <div class="about-item text-center">
                                <i class="fa fa-globe"></i>
                                <h3>AIM</h3>
                                <hr>
                                <p>
                                    The aim of lernen is to provide accessible and flexible educational opportunities to learners through digital technologies. Lernen allows learners to access a range of courses, educational materials, and learning resources online, anytime and anywhere. Lernen offer courses and training programs that focus on developing specific skills, such as coding, data analysis, and digital marketing.
                                </p>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                        <div class="col-md-4">
                            <div class="about-item text-center">
                                <i class="fa fa-pencil"></i>
                                <h3>MOTTO</h3>
                                <hr>
                                <p>
                                    The main motto of lernen is to make education accessible to everyone, regardless of their location, background, or schedule. Lernen aim to provide learners with the flexibility and convenience of learning at their own pace, on their own schedule, and from wherever they choose. Another important motto of lernen is to provide learners with affordable educational options.
                                </p>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>
    <div>
        <%- include('footer'); %>
    </div>
</body>

</html>